snippet.title: 6 Months Needed to Replenish Rs 500 Notes, Says Congress leader Randeep Singh Surjewala

localized.description:
Around six months needed to replenish Rs 500 notes, says Congress leader Randeep Singh Surjewala. On the other hand Modi government is claiming that there is no shortage of Rs 500 and Rs 2000 notes.
